Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.89,0:00:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name's Conan Edogawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.73,0:00:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,High school student Shinichi was forced\Nto take a pill that shrunk him!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.06,0:00:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I may look like a little\Ngrade school student,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.98,0:00:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but my powers of deduction\Nare unrivaled!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.98,0:00:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you how mysteries\Nare really solved!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.99,0:00:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today's incident is a terrifying\Nexplosion on a bullet train!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.74,0:00:21.19,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The first end of the century in 100 years{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.83,0:00:27.41,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When told to cry, I laughed instead{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.03,0:00:39.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The first end of the century\Nin a long, long time{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.18,0:00:45.59,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We're leaping into a wide open world{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.17,0:00:52.18,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The things I tried to\Nunderstand as a child{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.34,0:00:58.61,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}remain a mystery even as an adult{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.89,0:01:04.61,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm neither a hotshot\Nnor especially great{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.89,0:01:11.03,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All I understand is\Nthe pounding of my heart{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.19,0:01:16.92,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's neither an answer nor the truth{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.20,0:01:23.00,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All I have faith in is\Nthe pounding of my heart{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.29,0:01:28.51,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That and nothing else {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.08,0:01:50.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Great Bullet Train Explosion
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.80,0:02:01.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody shaves in the bullet train
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.14,0:02:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,on the way to their\Nbest friend's wedding!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.43,0:02:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not my fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.98,0:02:09.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I overslept 'cuz I was up late last\Nnight discussing things with a client!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.23,0:02:13.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, please. You got drunk\Nand fell asleep in the doorway.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.90,0:02:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I brought you along 'cuz you\Nwanted to come, but I dunno why...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.15,0:02:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the wedding's in Kyoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.20,0:02:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really wanted to go there too,\Ndidn't you, Conan-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.95,0:02:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.37,0:02:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did we have to\Nbring him along anyway?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.79,0:02:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know we can't\Nleave him all alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.33,0:02:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, are those new shoes?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.96,0:02:36.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Professor Agasa gave them to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.63,0:02:38.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I made you something\NI'm sure you'll like!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.30,0:02:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Power Kick Shoes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.89,0:02:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kick a ball with these shoes
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.93,0:02:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the criminals\Nwon't know what hit them!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.10,0:02:48.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It uses electricity and magnetic fields\Nto stimulate your feet muscles,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.81,0:02:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,thereby substantially\Nincreasing your kick power!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.40,0:02:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about my glasses?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.52,0:02:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're ready too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.48,0:02:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I added a miniature hidden\Nmicrophone to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.15,0:02:59.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm certain it'll come in handy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.74,0:03:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope they actually work\Nwhen I need them to!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.83,0:03:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A bullet train!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.16,0:03:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why are they with us too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.53,0:03:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does it matter?\NTheir tickets have been paid for.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.87,0:03:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, parents these days...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.37,0:03:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-kun! Let's go exploring!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.25,0:03:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like it'll be really fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.83,0:03:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.71,0:03:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their parents obviously have some issues.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.22,0:03:31.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what about his parents?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.80,0:03:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They haven't even called us once!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.68,0:03:34.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.81,0:03:36.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I gotta go to the bathroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.77,0:03:39.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I'm living\Nwith you because I want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.89,0:03:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all their fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.06,0:03:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were the ones who forced me\Nto take that weird pill
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.98,0:03:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and wind up small like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.86,0:03:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's them!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.17,0:04:05.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my best chance to\Nsteal some of those pills!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.96,0:04:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once I turn back into high\Nschool detective Shinichi Kudo,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.30,0:04:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll expose all of your\Nevil deeds to the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.89,0:04:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just you wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.64,0:04:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what in the world\Ncould they be doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.53,0:04:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're meeting with someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.12,0:04:46.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now's my chance to plant Professor\NAgasa's hidden microphone
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.67,0:04:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,on one of their seats!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.88,0:05:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Conan-kun?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.47,0:05:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.47,0:05:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't doing anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.76,0:05:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.85,0:05:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a troublemaker,\NConan-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.52,0:05:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's people like you who\Ngive kids a bad name!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.65,0:05:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should wrap the gum in paper\Nand put it in an ashtray!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.32,0:05:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.49,0:05:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll hear them just fine\Nif it's in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.49,0:05:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Learn from your friends, Conan-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.83,0:05:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're all such good children!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.91,0:05:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course we are!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.54,0:05:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.33,0:05:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I know you, Conan-kun,\Nthat wasn't any ordinary prank!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.63,0:05:41.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was that gum some sort\Nof secret weapon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.92,0:05:44.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are those two men spies?! Hit men?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.80,0:05:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would be great if they were,\Nbut I was just being a troublemaker!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.47,0:05:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For reals?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.64,0:05:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, man...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.19,0:05:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a bore.\NLet's get back to exploring!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.86,0:06:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me for being a bore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.82,0:06:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Outta the way, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.01,0:06:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.93,0:06:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not them!\NThey're not the men in black!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.31,0:06:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got the wrong people!\NI feel like such an idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.45,0:06:34.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He has a suitcase instead of\Nthe attach√© case he had before...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.42,0:06:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something's not right...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.42,0:06:46.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The two suitcases are too different
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.76,0:06:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for someone to accidentally\Nmistake one for the other...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.01,0:06:53.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it! I'll use the professor's\Nhidden microphone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.76,0:06:56.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said that if I turn the dial\Nto match the frequency,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.14,0:06:58.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,special sound waves will\Nstimulate my eardrums,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.27,0:07:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,allowing me to hear\Nwith my glasses on!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.73,0:07:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can finally have a smoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.32,0:07:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can hear them!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.24,0:07:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something's in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.24,0:07:12.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.49,0:07:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's just gum.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.49,0:07:16.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was close!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.54,0:07:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This sure turned out to be\Nan easy transaction, boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.54,0:07:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep it down!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.67,0:07:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, nobody's listening!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.29,0:07:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But 100 million just for\Nhanding over that case?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.79,0:07:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world was inside it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.17,0:07:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Information about gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.30,0:07:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Information that's worth more than\N100 million once it's put to use.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.05,0:07:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably's already sitting\Nback down, smiling with glee
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.51,0:07:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and looking out at the last scenic view\Nthat the fool will ever get to see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.27,0:07:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Last scenic view?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.14,0:07:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Included inside the black\Ncase we handed over...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.77,0:07:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...was a bomb that'll detonate in 10\Nseconds after receiving a large shock!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.32,0:07:58.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A bomb?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.61,0:08:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So if they accidentally\Ndrop the case...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.87,0:08:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The information is too important.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.37,0:08:08.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt that would happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.33,0:08:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And besides, the explosion\Nis set for 3:10.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.58,0:08:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a time bomb?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.83,0:08:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. But when the time comes,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.63,0:08:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they'll unknowingly press\Nthe detonation button themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.42,0:08:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,10 seconds later, the entire bullet\Ntrain gets blasted into pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.47,0:08:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Into pieces?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.02,0:08:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, 8 times 8 equals?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.40,0:08:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,64!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.02,0:08:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you mean "Happa 64"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.94,0:08:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.11,0:08:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,8 times 8 is 64!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.70,0:08:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,8 times 9...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.70,0:08:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,72!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.62,0:08:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid kid had me scared\Nthere for a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.00,0:08:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now arriving at Nagoya!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.63,0:08:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry! We're getting off!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.29,0:09:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! There's still something\NI want to ask you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.17,0:09:09.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.13,0:09:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not so fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.93,0:09:15.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let you out of\Nmy sight, Conan-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.06,0:09:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad! Without them onboard--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.60,0:09:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait. The person they made\Nthe transaction with is still inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.82,0:09:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, man! 40 minutes until it explodes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.82,0:09:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to find the person before then!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.03,0:09:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But how?! There's hundreds\Nof passengers onboard!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.62,0:09:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.42,0:09:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where could he have gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.43,0:10:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A bomb?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.52,0:10:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Someone onboard has a bomb!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.23,0:10:04.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to stop the train\Nat the next station
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.73,0:10:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and evacuate all the passengers!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.52,0:10:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This train's gonna be\Nblown to smithereens!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.53,0:10:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now. Don't be teasing grownups.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.11,0:10:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on. It isn't nice to disregard\Nhim just because he's a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.74,0:10:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second while I call\NAnpan Man for help!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.67,0:10:28.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No good! They don't\Nbelieve me one bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.13,0:10:29.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.84,0:10:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-kun! Is anything\Ninteresting going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.67,0:10:34.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us know if you find\Nanother case to solve!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.18,0:10:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are these the only guys\Nwho'll listen to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.64,0:10:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are tons of black briefcases...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.31,0:10:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Checking them all would be impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.48,0:10:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn it! Is my only option\Nto look for the bomb alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.99,0:10:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find a clue!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.61,0:10:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember back to the beginning\Nof their conversation!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.36,0:11:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can finally have a smoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.40,0:11:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.86,0:11:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The dining car isn't non-smoking...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.70,0:11:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! The person they met\Ndoesn't like cigarette smoke!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.87,0:11:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meaning that person doesn't smoke!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.66,0:11:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means the person's\Nin a non-smoking car!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.00,0:11:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see, how many non-smoking\Ncars were on this train...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.38,0:11:21.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eight!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.55,0:11:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.30,0:11:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are we solving a mystery?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.84,0:11:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There have to be more clues!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.47,0:11:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,100 million just for handing\Nover that case?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.47,0:11:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world was inside it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.89,0:11:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Information about gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.23,0:11:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably's already sitting\Nback down, smiling with glee
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.77,0:11:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and looking out at the last scenic view\Nthat the fool will ever get to see...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.32,0:11:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where on this train can you see\Nscenic views from the windows?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.32,0:11:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The 2-story Green Cars!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.95,0:11:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are 3 Green Cars, right?\NWhich ones are non-smoking?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.62,0:11:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That would be the 2nd floor of Car 7!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.83,0:11:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.04,0:11:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I dunno what's goin' on,\Nbut let's go anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.37,0:11:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's too dangerous for children...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.42,0:12:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're the Junior Detective Club!\NLet's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.56,0:12:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who could have the black briefcase\Nwith the bomb in it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.48,0:12:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.44,0:12:25.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.32,0:12:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.32,0:12:29.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Four...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.58,0:12:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to check them\Neach one by one!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.88,0:12:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stock trading and a gold Rolex!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.45,0:12:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's rakin' in the dough, all right...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.83,0:12:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.46,0:12:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Can I play that game too?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.59,0:12:53.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is not a toy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.13,0:12:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Liar! There's a bunch of circles\Nand rectangles on the screen!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.80,0:12:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're disrupting my work! Go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.01,0:12:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big meanie!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.84,0:13:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let me play this black one!\NIt's a game too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.60,0:13:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, little boy?\NAre you lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.19,0:13:14.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.07,0:13:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a good view this is!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.24,0:13:21.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it? The weather is clear today,\Nso you can see Mt. Fuji from there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.41,0:13:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mt. Fuji?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.37,0:13:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you like Mt. Fuji?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.91,0:13:28.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! I love it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.42,0:13:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn! It's locked!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.71,0:13:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up already! What part of\N"go away" don't you understand?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.76,0:13:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.54,0:13:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, did you go to the dining car?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.84,0:13:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Why do you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.00,0:13:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just thought you looked\Nlike the person who was there
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.92,0:13:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with some men dressed in black.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.26,0:13:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you must have\Nthe wrong person then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.30,0:13:51.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't been to the dining car.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.22,0:13:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, Mister?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.56,0:13:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As if I could go anywhere\Nwhen I'm this busy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.14,0:13:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.53,0:14:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, did you go to the dining\Ncar a little while ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.70,0:14:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.66,0:14:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said, did you go to the\Ndining car a little while ago?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.87,0:14:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, yes I did!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.79,0:14:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how many times I go,\NDisneyland is always fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.29,0:14:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't working out.\NI'll come back to him later!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.31,0:14:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold rims!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.77,0:14:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Did you go to the dining car?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.69,0:14:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.11,0:14:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's really none\Nof my business, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.20,0:14:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a napkin from the dining car!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.37,0:14:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy's been there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.41,0:14:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.29,0:15:02.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, my paper airplane\Ngot stuck up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.46,0:15:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't mind if I get it, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.38,0:15:05.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.92,0:15:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where is it?\NI can't find it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.34,0:15:13.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't touch that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.39,0:15:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Included inside the black case\Nwe handed over...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.06,0:15:23.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...was a bomb that'll detonate in\N10 seconds after receiving a large shock!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.81,0:15:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.24,0:15:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice catch, Genta-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.49,0:15:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excellent job!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.04,0:15:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.37,0:15:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.50,0:15:44.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you knock it off already?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.05,0:15:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Underwear?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.46,0:15:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You lousy kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.51,0:16:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And stay out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.39,0:16:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-kun! The rest of you too!\NGive it a rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.27,0:16:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,14 minutes until it explodes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.65,0:16:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's one person down!\NOnly three to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.07,0:16:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who has the bomb?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.03,0:16:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn those freaks!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.24,0:16:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a time bomb?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.08,0:16:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. But when the time comes,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.87,0:16:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they'll unknowingly press\Nthe detonation button themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.38,0:16:36.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.63,0:16:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means the explosion's set off by\Nthe person's reaction to something...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.59,0:16:45.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The 3 people have a laptop,\Na cell phone, and a tape player!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.64,0:16:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No good! They're all suspect!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.35,0:16:50.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still missing something!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.89,0:16:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No you don't! Where do\Nyou think you're going?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.98,0:16:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you to sit here\Nand behave yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.21,0:17:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I need to go to the bathroom...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.00,0:17:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just went.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.84,0:17:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm thirsty--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.84,0:17:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just put up with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.09,0:17:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gifts?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.05,0:17:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're supposed to buy\Nthose on your way back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.76,0:17:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A walk?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.76,0:17:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.68,0:17:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure do like\Nto get into trouble...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.56,0:17:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! 7 minutes left!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.10,0:17:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only choice now\Nis to explain everything
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.48,0:17:21.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and have all the passengers evacuate!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.94,0:17:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But nobody'll believe me\Nbecause I'm a kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.61,0:17:28.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's only one way\Nto make her believe me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.99,0:17:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I tell her that\NI'm actually Shinichi Kudo,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.41,0:17:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran would have to believe me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.24,0:17:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone would believe\Nher if she told them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.25,0:17:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the bomb explodes, me, Ran,\Nand all the other passengers are...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.09,0:17:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.84,0:17:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's no way to address your elders!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.26,0:17:54.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're supposed to use name\Nsuffixes for older people!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.31,0:17:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me, Ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.93,0:17:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.48,0:18:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.69,0:18:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.15,0:18:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been hiding something\Nfrom you this whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.86,0:18:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiding?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.28,0:18:10.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm neither Conan Edogawa\Nnor a grade school student!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.57,0:18:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.74,0:18:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.45,0:18:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did we pass the ocean already?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.45,0:18:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, while you were looking away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.54,0:18:22.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But these seats face the mountains!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.17,0:18:23.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We wouldn't have seen it anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.42,0:18:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Facing the mountains?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.33,0:18:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a good view this is!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.08,0:18:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it? The weather is clear today\Nso you can see Mt. Fuji from there!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.54,0:18:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure those seats\Nfaced the ocean!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.80,0:18:36.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would be impossible\Nto see Mt. Fuji!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.55,0:18:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then where did she see\NMt. Fuji from?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.51,0:18:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The dining car!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.10,0:18:47.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They sat on the side\Nfacing the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.77,0:18:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If she mistook the view from there\Nfor the view from her seat...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.94,0:18:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't been to the dining car.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.61,0:18:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that was a lie to cover up\Nthe truth about the transaction...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.49,0:19:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...then the bomb's...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.37,0:19:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...in her briefcase!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.58,0:19:10.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not good! Only one minute left!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.96,0:19:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attention, passengers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.84,0:19:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As using cellular phones may\Ndisturb other passengers,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.17,0:19:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we ask that you step onto the outside\Ndeck before using your phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.22,0:19:25.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it! The cell phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.85,0:19:28.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now what?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.85,0:19:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Ran says she'll buy us\Nany yummy food we want!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.40,0:19:35.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! I'll take\Nan eel boxed lunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.94,0:19:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want sushi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.32,0:19:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like a full course\Nof French cuisine!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.15,0:19:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.24,0:19:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible to plan for someone\Nto press a key or button
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.58,0:19:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,on a laptop or tape player\Nat exactly 3:10!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.12,0:19:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But a phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.66,0:19:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's entirely possible to have\Na predetermined time or phone number!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.83,0:20:02.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.71,0:20:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.50,0:20:09.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,10 seconds later, the entire bullet\Ntrain gets blasted into pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.44,0:20:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.53,0:20:31.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Who are you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.28,0:20:34.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan Edogawa. A detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.66,0:20:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Detective?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.87,0:20:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you! What have\Nyou done this time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.58,0:20:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just a grade school student though!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.17,0:20:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Afterward, the bullet train was stopped
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.59,0:20:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and Inspector Megure and his men\Nbegan their investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.76,0:20:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Being late to the wedding\Nwas a problem in itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.76,0:20:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but things somehow came to an end\Nwithout anyone getting hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.72,0:21:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It turns out she bought inside\Ninformation about the trading market
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.39,0:21:04.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,from the two men for 100 million yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.52,0:21:07.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, she was supposed\Nto call them on a specific phone
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.20,0:21:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,at a specific time to find out\Nhow to open the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.53,0:21:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the two planned from the start\Nto get rid of her after getting the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.28,0:21:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were caught and arrested\Nby an emergency police inspection line.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.29,0:21:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really jumped to conclusions though...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.46,0:21:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did the real men\Nin black who shrunk me go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.64,0:21:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn it! I'll never give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.55,0:21:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll catch up to you someday!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.30,0:21:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I swear it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.46,0:21:57.88,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just my imagination {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.00,0:22:07.63,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Playing with threads around my finger\Nwhile drinking lukewarm tea{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.35,0:22:16.69,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's walk lightly\Nto the bossa nova rhythm{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.81,0:22:21.69,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The puzzle pieces are in my hands{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.90,0:22:27.99,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.11,0:22:37.83,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was in the same place last week\Nbut with different clothes{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.17,0:22:45.26,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Step by step,\Nthere's no reason to be anxious{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.17,0:22:51.68,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Case by case,\NI don't care if you laugh{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.10,0:23:01.44,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Beyond the countless days,\Nshe's waiting for me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.86,0:23:05.99,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I gotta go my own way {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.79,0:23:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Conan-kun. What were you\Nabout to tell me that one time?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.21,0:23:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.63,0:23:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't pretend you don't know!\NYou were serious when you said it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.09,0:23:29.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm neither Conan Edogawa\Nnor a grade school student!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.26,0:23:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.43,0:23:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.85,0:23:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you actually?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.18,0:23:38.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, I'm actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.31,0:23:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A genius at getting into trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.29,0:24:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}What are you doing, Ran?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.31,0:24:10.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}It's chocolate. For Valentine's Day,\N{\a6}which only comes once a year!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.67,0:24:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A date?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.29,0:24:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going now!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.20,0:24:17.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go and catch a rich man.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.16,0:24:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It goes without saying that\Nthis case is an easy one.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.26,0:24:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means you did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.03,0:24:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The real murderer was...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.44,0:24:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next Conan--
